#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the Route pull-down</h2>
The Route pull-down has the following options:
<ul>
<li>Download - downloads a <a href="Route_sheet.cgi">route sheet</a> suitable for printing.
<li>E-mail route to <i>driver</i> - e-mail route to <i>driver</i>, suitable for printing.
<li><a href="order_Route.cgi">View or reorder route</a>
</ul>
<a href="Route_sheet.cgi">Route sheets</a> include a link (visible in your browser or e-mail) and QR code (visible on the printed sheet)
pointing to software that the driver can run en-route to
log progress and mileage.

